{
  "stem": "25423.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because all through my schooling, I missed Saturdays.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was not a very good student.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was always observed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So my memories are mixed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the teachers and other students.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because being my father's son, I was expected to perform in a competent and remarkable way, which I wasn't able to do.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "End of story.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After religion was introduced to the curriculum in the second grade, the Roman Catholics were instructed by a Roman Catholic priest, the Lithuanian by a Greek Catholic priest, and the Jews by a teacher of religion.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the minute religion was introduced, you had first signs of anti-semitism and friction between the kids.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Poles antagonistic toward the Lithuanians, who were Greek Catholic, Byzantine Catholics, and both against Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Fights, very simple.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, many.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it's a long story and, frankly, not interesting, because this was a way of life.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A Jew had to defend himself, or be beaten up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, because I used to beat up others.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was rather a scrappy little boy, and knew how to defend myself.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And occasionally, I ran into difficulties.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was exposed to anti-semitism and direct attacks, since the age of, probably, eight.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's way of life.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Jewish boys played together, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the introduction of religion, it ended.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had some--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The usual-- played ball.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With boys.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we used to go to the park.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the normal, [INAUDIBLE] to wander through the city, which was very interesting because very beautiful city with many things to offer.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's all I can tell you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was nothing unusual.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Until religion was introduced.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Eight, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After, no, because in the introduction of religion, was immediately segregated the children and introduced barriers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
